import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ApiService } from '../service/api.service'; import { FormBuilder,FormGroup,Validators } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-productview', templateUrl: './productview.component.html', styleUrls: ['./productview.component.css'] }) export class ProductviewComponent implements OnInit{ productlist!:any; editproduct!:any; editform!:any; constructor(private api:ApiService,private fb:FormBuilder){ } ngOnInit(): void { this.api.getlist().subscribe((x)=>{ console.log(x); this.productlist=x; }); this.editform=this.fb.group({ pid:[this.editform.pid,[Validators.required]], Pname: [this.editform.pname, [Validators.required]], description: [this.editform.description, [Validators.required, Validators.maxLength(100)]], Price: [this.editform.price, [Validators.required, Validators.pattern('')]], Qty: [this.editform.qty, [Validators.required, Validators.pattern('')]], Photo: [this.editform.photo, [Validators.required]] }) } edit(id:number,index:number){ //alert(id); var data=this.productlist[index]; // alert(data) this.editproduct=data; console.log(data); } delete(id:number){ alert(id); } submiteditform(){ } }
